      "author": {
        "id": 8223
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-09-26T03:54:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It is, but I think it\u0027s fine. I can already write a plain text file starting with \"GIF89a is a wonderful format\", but that\u0027s not a valid GIF file, even if it passes the previous (stricter) magic sniff test.",
      "parentUuid": "d76b189c_8d2faf42",
