      "writtenOn": "2018-09-25T19:52:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Should this update fPreviousBestNumFullyReceived? And then seekFrame can call this method?\n\nOtherwise it seems like fPreviousBestNumFullyReceived could be out of date, although it looks like no other method reads it.\n\nNow that I look at it further, it seems that seekFrame doesn\u0027t actually want the result. It\u0027s just deliberate that it does the updating, but this method still looks at the latest value. I don\u0027t understand why, though.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 515,
        "startChar": 23,
        "endLine": 515,
        "endChar": 39
      },
      "revId": "eac8a3e735325e1bc59d1800a4c166e147204475",
